Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.49,0:00:20.17,Dialogue,Asu,0,0,90,,It's done!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.49,0:00:19.43,Dialogue,Asu,0,0,90,,It's done!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.15,0:00:23.99,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,Since I had nothing prepared, I just let the chocolate melt and then freeze it back into a new shape.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.22,0:00:25.78,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,I wonder if she will be happy...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.32,0:00:28.15,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,Valentine chocolate!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.97,0:00:31.97,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,I really want to give this out already, to my favorite...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.85,0:00:35.77,Dialogue,Teacher,0,0,90,,Yamada Kyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.88,0:00:37.60,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.61,0:00:42.70,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,Hooray!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.70,0:00:44.21,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,Even though you sleep the entire day...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.96,0:00:48.20,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,Onee-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.56,0:01:02.25,Dialogue,Opening,0,0,90,,Mother went to heaven the year she gave birth to Asu.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.84,0:01:05.97,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,Father left a huge debt after gambling and is now missing,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.79,0:01:09.69,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,leaving only the two of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.11,0:01:12.56,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,The place we live in is
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.56,0:01:14.71,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,a beaten up 40 year old apartment with one room and no bath.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.23,0:01:17.12,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,This is our home.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.60,0:01:19.75,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,But, when spring comes...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.66,0:02:56.61,Dialogue,Title,0,0,90,,A Day of Jealousy, Chocolate, and Valentine's Day
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.08,0:03:09.81,Dialogue,Kyo,0,0,90,,It's all right! Just leave it up to Onee-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.13,0:03:14.93,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,From school to work, that's what Onee-chan says.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.21,0:03:18.04,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,It's really tough, actually.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.04,0:03:20.03,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,But she always keeps up a smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.00,0:03:24.19,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,This is the first time I've ever made chocolate for Onee-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.49,0:03:26.52,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,How should I give this to her...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.95,0:03:31.10,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,"Thank you for everything!" sounds a little strange...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.80,0:03:36.58,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,3:30, eh...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.44,0:03:40.07,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,Oh yeah, I should go pick up Onee-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.46,0:04:21.69,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,She hasn't come out yet... Onee-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.32,0:04:25.62,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,Maybe she's left school already...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.79,0:05:07.15,Dialogue,Kyo,0,0,90,,Please accept this!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.30,0:05:10.16,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,Um... about that...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.72,0:05:13.37,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,Please accept this chocolate!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.42,0:05:17.44,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,And then, please read the letter inside. I beg you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.65,0:05:20.49,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,Good bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.08,0:05:39.79,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,Onee-chan... already has someone she likes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.33,0:05:56.55,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,What should I do with this chocolate...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.36,0:06:13.30,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,I'm back!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.80,0:06:21.10,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,I'm hungry... what's for dinner tonight?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.68,0:06:46.17,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,Even though it's Onee-chan... it's normal that she has someone she likes, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.45,0:06:48.44,Dialogue,Kyo,0,0,90,,Asu?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.19,0:06:49.95,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,Asu!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.92,0:06:53.25,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,What's wrong? Spacing out like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.48,0:06:56.17,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,No... nothing at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.75,0:06:57.99,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.04,0:07:01.71,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,All right, Onee-chan will help you with those.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.71,0:07:04.78,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,It's fine, I can do it myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.78,0:07:07.02,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,Nah, here, let me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.02,0:07:08.56,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,I said it's fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.31,0:07:13.22,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,Asu...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.22,0:07:17.44,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,So-sorry. It's fine, I can do this myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.44,0:07:19.39,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,Onee-chan should go get some rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.73,0:07:22.06,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,If Asu says so... then okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.23,0:07:54.27,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,I don't think I can give it to her anymore... my chocolate...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.60,0:08:16.51,Dialogue,Students,0,0,90,,Did you guys see the soccer game from yesterday?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.51,0:08:18.09,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,I did, I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.48,0:08:22.81,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,The opponent wasn't that strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.02,0:08:24.85,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,It's the person that Onee-chan likes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.29,0:08:28.27,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,I couldn't help it, but the other team was a bit cheap.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.27,0:08:32.95,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,I wonder what kind of a person he is...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.50,0:08:36.40,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,As her younger sister, I have to find out.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.57,0:08:38.71,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,I'm back!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.43,0:08:48.05,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,Asu isn't back yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.09,0:08:53.09,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,Ahahaha... welcome back.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.14,0:09:08.86,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,There're club activities tomorrow, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.86,0:09:09.98,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,Yes, that's correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.98,0:09:11.59,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,Let's try hard tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.88,0:09:16.59,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,Good bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.59,0:09:19.24,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,See you tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.24,0:09:21.28,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,He has quite a number of friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.49,0:09:22.43,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,Good bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.45,0:09:49.00,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,He helped that grandma carry her suitcase.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.56,0:09:52.42,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,Ah, he even helped her up the stairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.27,0:09:57.35,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,He... might be a good person.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.62,0:10:04.85,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,But, but, but! This isn't enough, I can't hand over my sister just yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.54,0:10:08.29,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,Ah, he let his seat to a pregnant woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.74,0:10:12.98,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,Ah, he gave the wallet he found to the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.98,0:10:16.55,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,Ah, he got back the balloon that the kid lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.80,0:10:20.22,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,Ah, he's giving directions to a lost foreigner.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.79,0:10:25.41,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,No, no! That's still not enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.49,0:10:28.73,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,I still can't accept him with only these reasons.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.99,0:10:44.31,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,I must find out his true self.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.93,0:11:18.58,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,Ah, he even recycles.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.58,0:11:21.52,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,How is this possible... he's too perfect!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.17,0:11:40.34,Dialogue,Eyecatch,0,0,90,,(The neighboring town has meat to eat, so the distance doesn't seem too far.)
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.34,0:11:48.38,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,(We got off two stations early and finally bought meat with the money we saved this month.)
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.64,0:12:01.42,Dialogue,Asu,0,0,90,,He's a good person.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.72,0:12:04.82,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,No wonder Onee-chan likes him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.25,0:12:11.67,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,Hmmm... just what am I doing....
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.92,0:12:23.68,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,Eh? Onee-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.09,0:12:26.52,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,I'm... I'm back.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.73,0:12:28.83,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,Welcome back.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.25,0:12:38.34,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.68,0:12:39.73,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,Ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.67,0:12:41.87,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,I found it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.31,0:12:46.66,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,You were acting a little strange since yesterday... I wanted to ask what was wrong...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.14,0:12:49.81,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,This chocolate must be the reason, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.81,0:12:51.95,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,Hey hey, who are you giving this to?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.95,0:12:53.61,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,It couldn't have been... me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.66,0:12:58.39,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,Onee-chan doesn't even want my chocolate, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.39,0:12:58.98,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.38,0:13:03.10,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,Yesterday you gave chocolate to a guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.10,0:13:03.73,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,Ah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.30,0:13:06.63,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,You saw that, Asu?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.77,0:13:10.43,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,One day... one day... Onee-chan will go to that person's side...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.74,0:13:11.94,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,Leaving me all alone...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.65,0:13:15.55,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,You don't even want my chocolate, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.55,0:13:16.39,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,Asu!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.41,0:13:25.42,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,Onee-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.76,0:13:30.27,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,Onee-chan won't accept my chocolate.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.00,0:13:55.91,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,Maybe... I can't ever give chocolates to Onee-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.70,0:14:12.69,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,Even if she accepts it,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.09,0:14:16.03,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,she'll just say that she's glad to get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.83,0:14:20.08,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,But... she won't be truly happy, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.32,0:14:26.38,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,Because... Onee-chan already has someone she likes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.00,0:14:30.35,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,I'm just an annoying child...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.26,0:14:33.27,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,Asu...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.54,0:14:49.72,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,I think I really should cheer Onee-chan on...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.33,0:14:53.68,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,What is this feeling...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.24,0:15:21.11,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,Ah, it's that person.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.34,0:15:26.30,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,Who's he waiting for...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.01,0:15:28.88,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,What if it's... Onee-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.79,0:15:56.45,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,Why... did he go off with another girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.83,0:15:57.88,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,Why...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.47,0:15:59.31,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,Asu!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.88,0:16:02.04,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,Asu!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.55,0:16:07.58,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,Onee-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.58,0:16:08.49,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,Asu!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.66,0:16:12.43,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,Thank goodness... so you were here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.52,0:16:14.28,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,Tha-thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.91,0:16:17.08,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,Um... Onee-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.50,0:16:21.07,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,I was just here... and then... um...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.34,0:16:22.24,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,Meat buns!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.93,0:16:24.70,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,Oh yeah, meat buns!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.82,0:16:28.54,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,I saw an advertisement that said there will be meat buns for sale at 10 yen each.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.54,0:16:32.01,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,10 yen!? Where was this ad?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.38,0:16:34.82,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,Oh no... I set the price too low.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.82,0:16:37.66,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,If we don't hurry, they'll get sold out.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.66,0:16:39.08,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,Hey, where are the advertisements?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.08,0:16:41.88,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,Um... that... uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.88,0:16:42.76,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,Over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.07,0:16:44.94,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,I understand. It's over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.94,0:16:46.43,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,Asu, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.39,0:16:53.51,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,Where is it advertised, Asu...?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.51,0:16:57.33,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,Uh... that... where was it again...?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.50,0:16:59.68,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,It probably sold out.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.68,0:17:01.99,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,Eh!? No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.41,0:17:05.73,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,I wanted to eat them with Asu...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.59,0:17:09.22,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,If she knew that the one she likes has a girlfriend already,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.39,0:17:11.57,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,Onee-chan will probably be very sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.16,0:17:18.40,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,No. He's the type of person who accepted the chocolate but went off with someone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.40,0:17:21.17,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,Those types of people are better off dumped by Onee-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.59,0:17:30.03,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,Ah! Uh... Onee-chan, that...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.85,0:17:31.73,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.63,0:17:37.67,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,I found it! The 10 yen meat buns!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.90,0:17:38.39,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.00,0:17:41.96,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,Ah! It's really 10 yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.67,0:17:46.35,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,You're amazing, Onee-chan. You really found it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.62,0:17:51.05,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,What are you talking about? You're the one that's amazing, because you found it first.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.21,0:17:57.58,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,Ah! Anyway, let's go in first.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.92,0:18:01.59,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,If they can pass us while we're entering this store than that'd be great.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.70,0:18:03.04,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,Welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.99,0:18:07.68,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,Um... are these meat buns really 10 yen a piece?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.68,0:18:10.31,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,Yes. Right now we're having a special promotion.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.52,0:18:12.03,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,Would you like to buy one?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.22,0:18:13.65,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,{\an8}Yes, please give me two.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.24,0:18:16.17,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,But... if she saw a picture of him holding another girl's hand...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.27,0:18:20.35,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,Onee-chan will probably not like him anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.87,0:18:22.47,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,If that happens... I...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.78,0:18:34.98,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,For Onee-chan's sake... What I can do...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.32,0:18:36.39,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,Onee-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.20,0:18:40.61,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,What's wrong, Asu?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.61,0:18:42.94,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,Onee-chan, since it's rare that we've come here,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.94,0:18:46.15,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,let's buy two more, so it's two for each of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.45,0:18:55.33,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,That's great, the two of you got together fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.54,0:19:01.69,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,Because I didn't say anything afterwards, I was worried about how it turned out.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.10,0:19:04.61,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,I see, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.61,0:19:06.25,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,I'm happy too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.36,0:19:07.72,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,That's great.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.83,0:19:11.06,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,If something happens later, tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.10,0:19:12.87,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,Yes, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.95,0:19:25.40,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,I gave that chocolate as a favor for one of my classmates.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.18,0:19:27.94,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,I-I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.83,0:19:33.13,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,I mistook it for something else... how embarrassing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.34,0:19:36.11,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,Sorry, tricking you like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.89,0:19:40.54,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,But, Asu.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.71,0:19:43.76,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,If you become worried later about something like this again,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.76,0:19:48.10,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,just remember that Onee-chan will not leave you alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.10,0:19:49.09,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,I definitely won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.19,0:19:54.74,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.78,0:20:09.76,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,But, Asu was worried about me, so I was happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.77,0:20:13.75,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,Eh? What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.33,0:20:15.40,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,I don't care anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.38,0:20:20.02,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,Ha, I'm sorry, you angry?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.15,0:20:20.86,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,I don't care.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.12,0:20:23.59,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,Ah, don't leave me alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.56,0:20:27.56,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,Thinking about someone else...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.79,0:20:30.27,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,Bringing that person a warm coat to wear...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.69,0:20:34.56,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,Then finding cheap meat buns to eat together...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.46,0:20:40.31,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,Once I think that Onee-chan will one day do such things for someone else,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.75,0:20:43.57,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,I feel a little sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.95,0:20:50.83,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,I think when that time comes, Onee-chan will definitely not leave me alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.61,0:20:55.37,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,So, even if I answered, "Yes", will that be fine?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.65,0:20:59.13,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,If... that time really comes...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.91,0:21:02.02,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,Anyway, Asu.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.97,0:21:05.55,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,Who are you giving this chocolate to anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.47,0:21:15.00,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,To my favorite person!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.35,0:21:19.77,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,Eh? Who's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.64,0:21:23.34,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,Wait up! Asu!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.34,0:21:25.34,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,Who is your favorite person?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.34,0:21:31.19,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,That's why... the choice I make... is the one that will bring happiness to favorite Onee-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.95,0:23:10.08,Dialogue,Preview,0,0,90,,I hear a ghost... a ghost's voice, Asu.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.08,0:23:12.90,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,It's... It's all right Onee-chan, I will be by your side.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.40,0:23:14.83,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,Binbou Shimai Monogatari
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.04,0:23:17.71,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,A Day of Guitars, Dreams and the Music Teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.96,0:23:19.30,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,Please watch it!